    <data key="d0">True Blue Serverless Data Lake Architecture</data>
    <data key="d1">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iKYvG5aiIn8</data>
    <data key="d2">Serverless data lake architecture utilizing AWS Glue to process database transactions and updates in near-real time instead of EMR.</data>
